        "author_role": "OWNER",
        "timestamp": "2019-03-08 13:20:24.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 3:\n\n> Jim, did you consider making the 2 methods one single one to avoid\n > some code duplication?\n\nI had originally thought about that, but the no-arg version will work without doing a DNS look-up, so I decided to leave it as two separate chunks of code.  Hence I had to include separate chunks of code to test them both, too.",
