        "author_role": "OWNER",
        "timestamp": "2019-03-08 13:21:22.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 3:\n\n> > Jim, did you consider making the 2 methods one single one to\n > avoid\n > > some code duplication?\n > \n > I had originally thought about that, but the no-arg version will\n > work without doing a DNS look-up, so I decided to leave it as two\n > separate chunks of code.  Hence I had to include separate chunks of\n > code to test them both, too.\n\nNevertheless, if you'd prefer I do that, then I will - probably just use \"localhost\" rather than looking up the machine name.",
